gedit-afc
Syntax highlighting for Tubaina's AFC format at gedit
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALLING ---------------------------------------------------------------------

First, place the tubaina.lang file at:
	~/.local/share/gtksourceview-2.0/language-specs.

Or in newer systems you might have to use:
	~/.local/share/gtksourceview-3.0/language-specs.

Or even directly under the folder bellow, to enable it for all users:
	/usr/share/gtksourceview-3.0/language-specs

Then start (or restart) gedit.

An entry for 'Tubaina' will be placed at: View -> Highlight Mode -> Markup.
